  "description": [
    "Gadsden County Citizens Council Holds Regular Meeting Dec 4 By John B Hayes The Gadsden County Citizens Council held its regular monthly meeting on December 4 Aldrich Blake Laguna Beach Calif is promoting an amend ment to the U S Constitution which is called The Freedom of Choice Amendment This proposed amendment consists of 8 sections 3 of which are given below Section 2 Places of Public Ac commodation The right of the owners and operators of all kind and description their agents servants and employees of all hotels restaurants inns cafes bars ice cream parlors soft drink stands motels apartment houses trailer camps cemeter ies dance halls skating rinks bath houses barber shops beau ty shops and other privately owned places of public accom odation or amusement to choose their own guests patrons and tenants shall not be abridged Section 3 Employment The right of every citizen to employ or not to employ other persons of his own free discretion shall not be abridged Nothing in this section shall be construed to impair the right of organized labor to contract or bargain col lectively Section 7 Schools Education al policies including adminis tration finance subject matter of instruction assignment"
  ],
